title: 330. Misconceptions Of Humility: How To Become An Effective Young Entrepreneur
itunes:title: 330. Misconceptions Of Humility: How To Become An Effective Young Entrepreneur
description: In today's episode, Andy talks about society's misconception regarding humility, why being a good follower translates well into being an effective leader, and how to fast-track your progression by learning from other people's mistakes.
